{"tid":1701214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前港府顧問：港人可眾籌到海牙法院仲裁警暴","createTime":"2019-11-09T02:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:35:20.000Z","uid":335207,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"25f28abef1637d375913a06fc19c633b56179f12","tid":1701214,"uid":335207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港特區政府中央政策組前成員練乙錚指出，香港問題目前正處於一個&ldquo;死局&rdquo;，北京也沒有明智的辦法解決香港的深層次矛盾，既然面對如此膠着局面，國際慣例就應找仲裁解決。他告訴蘋果日報，港府既然不敢惹毛下面的警察，不願意成立獨立調查委員會，港人大可眾籌將港警執法行為搬到獨立的海牙法院，由國際法庭對他們作出仲裁，判斷是否真的侵犯人權，將整件事件國際化。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他以南海紛爭為例指出，就算中方拒絕派出代表應訊，不承認裁決，美國卻藉此而更加大條道理派軍艦巡邏，中方反對也只是徒呼荷荷。<br />\n<br />\n練說，海牙的常設仲裁法院，已有百多年歷史，中國都是參與國之一。練說：&ldquo;我覺得香港人一個做法系可以到海牙提出仲裁，實際上你可以單方面提出，籌到錢就要求仲裁港警行為，逼政府接受裁決。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n香港在2011年6月已通過《香港仲裁條例》，讓法例能與國際仲裁製度接軌，目的是有意把香港發展成為國際仲裁中心。練說，因此就算海牙法院對港警執法行為作出不利的仲裁，特區政府都理應大方接受裁決，否則定會造成非常尷尬的局面。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，國際仲裁也好，獨立調查委員會也好，都是文明世界處理政治事件的慣常做法。練乙錚覺得，假如所有文明方法都不肯接受，證明林鄭根本就是一個野蠻政府，&ldquo;你看到現在很多法律以外的行為，很可能是政府或警察做。看看那麼多的浮屍，有沒有搞錯？1967年文化大革命以來，香港從來未試過有這麼密集的浮屍個案，你說是誰搞出來？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n當民主國家發生嚴重政治失誤，主事者理應問責下台，並非以暴制暴，釐清政治責任後，就由新人上台，重新洗牌，這是古今中外的慣例。可是，林鄭雖承認做錯，但就不肯問責下台，連犧牲一個半個管治班子都沒有，&ldquo;林鄭自己不肯負責，炒個律政司祭旗也好，令大家順氣一點，以證明有決心處理，但連這一步都不做，根本解決不了問題。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n由2014年中共強硬拒絕真普選開始，練乙錚覺得香港人並未完全灰心，只是一直在伺機爆發，但想不到年輕人現在展現出來的反抗力量，會是如此猛烈，完全超乎他想像。因此，如果這次中共再次強硬打壓港人聲音，以為靠拘捕就能平息民憤，他相信港人的反抗心態只會越來越激進。<br />\n<br />\n練說：&ldquo;我覺得運動已經進入准內戰狀態，如果有一日大陸解放軍（步）操下來香港，不再偷偷摸摸換衣服扮香港警察，明刀明槍鎮壓，到時就是一場內戰，要不香港全面投降，要不香港人就更加勇武抵抗。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n戰爭原本跟香港似乎相當遙遠，但近月再荒謬的事，香港人都一起經歷過，況且中共曾以解放軍威嚇，命運早已被刀架頸上。自1947年，中國就再無內戰，中共未曾打過台灣，處理新疆和西藏問題都是速戰速決，練乙錚強調，惟獨香港這戰場令中共最為頭痛：&ldquo;毛澤東都講過，『國家要獨立，民族要解放，人民要革命』，你越逼就越大件事，你自己中共不是最清楚嗎？共產黨固執就在這裡，以為香港地方細小容易搞，其實不是呀，邊疆所有棘手問題當中，香港這場仗打最久了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n練認為共產黨要開竅，才能真正解決問題，始終香港仍具獨特優勢，是中國在貿易戰惡鬥下，唯一未打爛的金蛋。他建議香港人要持續將所有問題國際化，例如舉行在即的區選，一定要將香港所有矛盾都呈現到全世界面前，絕不能任由政府關門打狗，&ldquo;延遲選舉這卑鄙手段完全可做得出，所以在這問題上不要受他挑釁，臨到選舉前全部靜下來，再邀請外國記者來港，將件事放到國際層面，甚至登廣告，讓全世界目光都集中到這次區選。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://rfi.my/4rGM.f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frfi.my%2F4rGM.f&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=c2d4fe6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rfi.my/4rGM.f</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有得搞，，應該好快籌到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11013b9418b42e3eccc79871b9d009906552d28","tid":1701214,"uid":67308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d7bb8edaad20de7699d765e7fa71434a5d0082","tid":1701214,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"真係得？"},{"pid":"8c0def7f58da048c76def3b9d2aab2ff0ff6a2ea","tid":1701214,"uid":156096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"*眾籌*<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先52%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=7110f95d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3f042cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790fdc81e0c5beeedaf6a40157f3c8d31ba38933","tid":1701214,"uid":335207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37d7bb8edaad20de7699d765e7fa71434a5d0082","tid":1701214,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"真係得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"唔知⋯⋯希望有巴打幫手研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2199db11f9d80ea6b902a77eec00b019823f72","tid":1701214,"uid":207574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b65eb054046fd737113646d91a707ba36c2d9f14","tid":1701214,"uid":11894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"推左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc78bb78590219e7adffd2f49060aff018aa490","tid":1701214,"uid":119489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61a43f576c56aca38397f3dc10187e2758f50147","tid":1701214,"uid":335207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.icj-cij.org/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fen&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=55e82225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icj-cij.org/en</a><br />\n<br />\n海牙國際法庭嘅page, 大家幫手搵下資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5791a9bd68939b5579f53164415efdc047c557f5","tid":1701214,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"錢我地大把 但有無國際戰線領頭羊？"},{"pid":"aec33b922d5b5f27d61330b24c6f9590a6d4d08b","tid":1701214,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"推到攬炒巴幫香港人申冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我雖然學生 但可以告我即捐5舊"},{"pid":"86f01ada610a3e732243bd6c0cb0d3a1a3d00f13","tid":1701214,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人拉頭?我50+認損$1500</span>"},{"pid":"ec08d4548f335ff0a71b427350b6357cf37ad61a","tid":1701214,"uid":335207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"希望攬炒巴會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5d29da55e5c468fb4b9a8ae332560eac38e664","tid":1701214,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（最新）Senator Rubio 出聲講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=dd4f55db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a><br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=42c1b2ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=229f373a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&h=01c0cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"432514edf1438a9e1a523c47efcde787420c59b1","tid":1701214,"uid":245841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72d7f56d5ef149916f3a8fed6d61563f254542c6","tid":1701214,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"認實 實課金"},{"pid":"23966329813ede9872376ad196cf703f097f471c","tid":1701214,"uid":197745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"趁呢個機會叫612比錢有無可能？"},{"pid":"801722eec7ac16ca6b4bed2ff66c63edfe123502","tid":1701214,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e275b039b780a43d29c560d5d0deb32bfe314ed9","tid":1701214,"uid":25505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"我會課金！推！"},{"pid":"d560fc4aa4d637d701eab325af98cc4e0bc0ecba","tid":1701214,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"燒山認證咗<br />\n快啲推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467a1176e008c1ed03163c1598fbc33a4d2abc5d","tid":1701214,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8a212592800b7dbed5bf447f0f9f41fb761f881","tid":1701214,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a650805eb0fb629a33cac620b3a1e0786c5c091","tid":1701214,"uid":267914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"我捐！"},{"pid":"f8396c09937c933f5d212721ce6b6a664a440de5","tid":1701214,"uid":176567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09c287cc7a77f1f116b7c06dca0e954735899cd4","tid":1701214,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"我記得一直有法律巴絲update警暴法律資料，有冇得搵人拎果份野去告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}